    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 78-81.</p><p>Arcane Exemplar</p><p>At 25th level, you gain an additional 9th-level spell slot (included on the class table), and you learn the ability to concentrate on an additional spell at a time. If your concentration is broken, all spells you were concentrating on end.</p><p>The number of spells you can concentrate on at a time can never exceed 4, even if you gain this same benefit from various sources.</p></div>",
